  "content": [
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Iker Casillas Fernández was born in Móstoles, Spain, just outside Madrid. He was raised there and also briefly in the Basque Country."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://uk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20100711154653AAA1heV",
      "sourceTitle": "Is Iker Casillas a Muslim?",
      "text": "Casillas' religion is a matter of much internet speculation, which teeters between Muslim and Catholic."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Religion_in_Spain",
      "sourceTitle": "Religion in Spain.",
      "text": "It seems more likely to me that he is Catholic, and not only because around 70% of Spaniards are devoted to that religion."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Islam_in_Spain",
      "sourceTitle": "Islam in Spain.",
      "text": "Casillas' parents are from Spain, and most of Spain's Muslim population are fairly recent immigrants."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Soccer/Euro/2012/06/28/19930351.html",
      "sourceTitle": "'Saint' Iker tops list of Spanish heroes.",
      "text": "He has also earned the nickname \"Saint Iker\" for his divine goalkeeping abilities,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "which says more about the religion of his country than of himself, although I couldn't find any indication that he minds the title."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "It's also entirely possible that Casillas is simply not religious at all. Or. . . he's established his own church under the guise of a . It's all speculation from here, folks. Leave us a comment if you can steer us toward some facts."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Soccer/Euro/2012/06/28/19930351.html",
      "sourceTitle": "'Saint' Iker tops list of Spanish heroes.",
      "text": "Casillas has equally little say about politics, aside from his hope that football can be a positive distraction from the bad economic news which relentlessly plagues his country."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.jimmy-burns.com/blog/politics/valdes-iker-casillas-politics-spain/",
      "sourceTitle": "Valdes, Iker Casillas, & the politics of Spain.",
      "text": "Although he doesn't appear to have anything to say about Catalan independence, at least one blogger thought that a Casillas transfer from Real Madrid to Barça could do more than politicians to quell the independence movement and restore civility between the two camps."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "My guess is that Casillas would rather not be a pawn for either side in the middle of that debate."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
